# ================================
# SECURITY NOTE
# ================================
# This file prevents committing:
# 1. Private keys (MOST IMPORTANT)
# 2. API keys
# 3. Database credentials
# 4. JWT secrets
# 5. Encryption keys
# 6. RPC URLs with API keys
# 7. Any .env files
#
# ALWAYS review files before committing!
# Use: git status
# Then: git diff <file>
